This track is recommended for you if you have a background in Humanities, or Social Science and wish to improve your academic research or if you like to find a job as a Data Scientist or Machine Learning Engineer.
In this track during week 1 - 2 you will be introduced to Python. From week 3 to 4 you will be introduced to Natural Language Processing and AI with Python. From Week 5 you can work on the previous courses for the rest of the summer to make a project of your own.
How else can I help you?
